
<div class="inner signup_page_inner">
  <div class="sub_heading_wrapper">
    <h1>Sign Up</h1>
    <p>Not happy? We offer a 100% money back within the first 48 hours of signing up.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <div class="left_column_forms">
      <div class="social_signup_wrapper">
        <h2>Sign Up Using Twitter or Facebook</h2>

        <div class="social_signup_button_wrapper">

          <a href="#" class="twitter_social_button">Sign up via <strong>Twitter</strong></a>

          <p>Or</p>

          <a href="#" class="fb_social_button">Sign up via <strong>Facebook</strong></a>

        </div>

        <p class="social_option_final_line">Don't want to use twitter or facebook you can sign up below</p>

      </div>

      <div class="login_ignup_form_wrapper">

        <h2>Your Details</h2>



        <%= simple_form_for @user do |f| %>
          <%= f.error_notification %>
          <%= f.input :email %>
          <%= f.input :password %>
          <%= f.input :password_confirmation %>
          <%= f.submit 'Sign up' %>
        <% end %>



        <input class="podmedics_textfield" type="text" placeholder="Name" />

        <input class="podmedics_textfield" type="text" placeholder="Email" />

        <input class="podmedics_textfield" type="password" placeholder="Password" />

        <input class="podmedics_textfield" type="password" placeholder="Password confirmation" />

      </div>


      <div class="billing_section">

        <h2>Billing</h2>

        <div class="billing_options">

          <input name="RadioGroup1" type="radio" id="RadioGroup1_0" value="radio" checked="checked" />
          <label for="RadioGroup1_0" class="active_label">Yearly billing<strong> £30 / A year</strong></label>


          <input name="RadioGroup1" type="radio" id="RadioGroup1_0" value="radio" checked="checked" />
          <label for="RadioGroup1_0" class="active_label">Yearly billing<strong> £30 / A year</strong></label>


          <input type="radio" name="RadioGroup1" value="radio" id="RadioGroup1_1" />
          <label for="RadioGroup1_1">Monthly Billing <strong>£2.50 / A Month</strong></label>


        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="red_button">Sign-up and proceed to payment</button>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="right_column_forms">
      <h3>Membership Info</h3>
      <p>There are over 150 medical video tutorials on Podmedics that cover topics throughout medicine, surgery and all the clinical specialties. </p>
      <p>We are also adding new ones all the time - at a rate of about one per week.</p>
      <p>Do feel free to drop us an email anytime at <a href="mailto:contact@podmedics.com"><strong>contact@podmedics.com</strong></a> and we would be delighted to give you any further information that you require.</p>
    </div>


  </div>



</div>






